{"id": "4606", "post": "<div class=\"post-4606 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-atlanta tag-bluevm-com tag-buffalo tag-chicago tag-dallas tag-exclusive tag-kansas-city tag-kvm tag-los-angeles tag-openvz tag-switzerland tag-usa tag-zurich\" id=\"post-4606\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/bluevm-18year-512mb-and-29-95year-1gb-kvm-in-los-angeles-or-buffalo/\" rel=\"bookmark\">BlueVM \u2013 $18/Year 512MB and $29.95/year 1GB KVM in Los Angeles or Buffalo</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/atlanta/\" rel=\"tag\">atlanta</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bluevm-com/\" rel=\"tag\">BlueVM.Com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buffalo/\" rel=\"tag\">buffalo</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/chicago/\" rel=\"tag\">chicago</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/dallas/\" rel=\"tag\">dallas</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kansas-city/\" rel=\"tag\">kansas city</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\" rel=\"tag\">kvm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/los-angeles/\" rel=\"tag\">los angeles</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/switzerland/\" rel=\"tag\">switzerland</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/usa/\" rel=\"tag\">USA</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/zurich/\" rel=\"tag\">zurich</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> November 8, 2013 @ 8:00 pm, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bluevm.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/BlueVM-Portal-Home-2013-11-09-03-32-40-300x191.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" alt=\"BlueVM\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/BlueVM-Portal-Home-2013-11-09-03-32-40-300x191.png.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"191\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Justin, from <a href=\"http://bluevm.com\" target=\"_blank\">BlueVM</a>, has sent in three very nice offers to us. These offers are exclusive to LowEndBox.com and all feature their own panel: Feathur. Feathur has a viewable/editable <a href=\"https://github.com/BlueVM/Feathur\">source</a>, is free for private use and was recently <a href=\"http://lowendtalk.com/discussion/16168/feathur-launch-vps-control-panel-0-6-0-1-free-for-private-use#latest\">launched in beta</a>.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>November KVM2<br>\n</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>2 CPU Cores</li><li>20GB Disk space</li><li>1TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>KVM/Feathur</li><li>$18/Year | <a href=\"https://www.bluevm.com/cart.php?gid=42\">Link</a></li><li>$25/Year in Zurich</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>November KVM3<br>\n</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>3 CPU Cores</li><li>30GB Disk space</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>KVM/Feathur</li><li>$29.95/Year | <a href=\"https://www.bluevm.com/cart.php?gid=42\">Link</a></li><li>$36.95/Year in Zurich</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>BLUE 0.5<br>\n</strong><p></p><ul><li>128MB RAM</li><li>128MB vSwap</li><li>1.0 Ghz+ CPU Core</li><li>5GB Disk space</li><li>100GB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>OpenVZ/Feathur</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://bluevm.com/tos.php?section=11\">Limited support!</a></strong></li><li>$7.50/Year | <a href=\"https://www.bluevm.com/cart.php?gid=42\">Link</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>BlueVM Communications LLC are based in Honolulu and are dedicated to offering \u201clow cost, high quality Virtual Private Servers (VPS)\u201d. We have featured BlueVM <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bluevm-com/\">numerous times</a> since early 2012 and reviews have been mainly positive. After they had enough of SolusVM after numerous security incidents, BlueVM decided to write their own panel. Feathur is the result of that. It\u2019s already in use at BlueVM (and has been for a while) but it is now also available to the public. Their hardware primarily consists of Intel E3-1240 servers (@ 3.4GHz) with 32 GB of RAM and 4 x 1TB or 2TB hard drives in&nbsp;RAID10. A review of their service (which includes Feathur screenshots &amp; serverbear link) can be <a href=\"http://lowendtalk.com/discussion/12558/bluevm-vps-review-blue1-1-mo-vps-special-loving-these-guys\">found here</a>.<br>\n<span id=\"more-4606\"></span><br>\nBlueVM accept PayPal, Google Checkout and Bitcoin via Bitpay. Due to abuse of their previous refund policy, they no longer offer refunds on their services except in special cases. They provide a 99.99% uptime guarantee and provide service credits if they fail to meet this. According to their website, they undersell (typically they leave 500GB of HDD space free and 2-4GB of ram free). For more information, have a read of their <a href=\"https://www.bluevm.com/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a>.</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Network Information:</span></p><p><strong>Zurich, Switzerland</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.zu.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.zu.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.zu.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Buffalo, NY, USA</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.ny.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.ny.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.ny.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Chicago, IL, USA</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.il.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.il.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.il.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Los Angeles, CA, USA</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.ca.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.ca.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.ca.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Atlanta, GA, USA</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.atl.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.atl.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.atl.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Dallas, TX, USA</strong> =&gt; Test IP: s1.tx.bluevm.com, <a href=\"http://s1.tx.bluevm.com/100mb.test\">http://s1.tx.bluevm.com/100mb.test</a></p><p><strong>Kansas City, MO, USA</strong> (Transfer upon request only)</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbluevm-18year-512mb-and-29-95year-1gb-kvm-in-los-angeles-or-buffalo%2F&amp;t=BlueVM%20-%20%2418%2FYear%20512MB%20and%20%2429.95%2Fyear%201GB%20KVM%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20or%20Buffalo\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=BlueVM%20-%20%2418%2FYear%20512MB%20and%20%2429.95%2Fyear%201GB%20KVM%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20or%20Buffalo&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbluevm-18year-512mb-and-29-95year-1gb-kvm-in-los-angeles-or-buffalo%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\